{
  "text": "Cox proportional hazards regression analysis was used for multivariate analysis. Discrimination of the nomogram was quantified with the concordance index. [CITATION_1] The concordance index is a modification of the area under the receiver operating characteristic curve (AUC). It was adapted to fit censored data. [CITATION_2] Its interpretation is similar to AUC.",
